info.author: Chitta Ranjan
info.name: sgt
info.summary: Sequence Graph Transform (SGT) is a sequence embedding function.                          SGT extracts the short- and long-term sequence features and embeds them                   in a finite-dimensional feature space. With SGT you can tune the amount                   of short- to long-term patterns extracted in the embeddings without any                   increase in the computation.
